anic is important, you should plan each movement since the very beginning not to fail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>+40 LEVELS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287530/extras/b5cdf0c6011c8a89cb93fe642140c4fb.poster.avif?t=1730479789\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287530/extras/b5cdf0c6011c8a89cb93fe642140c4fb.webm?t=1730479789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287530/extras/b5cdf0c6011c8a89cb93fe642140c4fb.mp4?t=1730479789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > With 40 initial levels, adding new maps with new obstacles in future updates and seasons <strong><i>completely free</i></strong>.</p>",
